ime":"2019-07-04T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"石田為業喜非常，<br />\n畫餅將來未見香；<br />\n怎曉田耕耘不得，<br />\n那知餅食不充腸。<br />\n<br />\n9up<br />\n某人得到1塊田 好開心， 點知係石田<br />\n畫啲唔香既野食 諗住遲下食， 點知田又種唔到， 野食又唔飽<br />\n<br />\n一場白做<br />\n<br />\n9up mode 屌細力啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:00:08.000Z","msg":"我好驚係指我哋白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"089a7219bd731776edcd07327500ef8df0e38aa5","tid":1285633,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:01:28.000Z","msg":"而家過咗半年<br />\n睇唔睇到下半年會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a627d665759a073126513693389aaf9024a02f4f","tid":1285633,"uid":159568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"常得香腸"},{"pid":"f5cbd388539d7c70e92ccff569370bc8eeb6bb92","tid":1285633,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"石田，意思是無法耕作的田，比喻毫無用處的物品。放在香港的背景，石田是「摘去鮮花，然後種出大廈」，似乎暗指樓市。香港以樓市為業，只升不跌的狂喜，惡怕並非常態。<br />\n<br />\n「田」字的讀音又令人聯想起填海的「填」，明日大嶼計劃寧將公帑萬憶倒落海，也不用作全民退保改善民生；寧可破壞郊野公園、綠化地帶，也不處理棕地、丁權問題。<br />\n<br />\n石田又令人想起，政府縱容土豪劣紳先破壞、後發展，在田野堆填建築廢料電子垃圾，造成嘉湖山丘的泥頭山，香園圍綠化農地變爛地，錦田十年變成石田。<br />\n<br />\n籤文提到「畫餅充饑」的故事，如在地上畫餅只能看不能食，比喻徒具形式毫無實用價值。「畫餅將來未見香」，明日大嶼、一帶一路等假大空、畫餅仔的計劃，前景未見樂觀；融入大灣區，更是令香港不復見的完結香港計劃。<br />\n<br />\n怎知以上石田畫餅之計耕耘不得，毫無收成。那所謂「做大個餅」的滴流效應，對普羅市民來說卻是食不充腸。所以市民寧願政府派錢，也不再相信政府畫餅充饑的空言。<br />\n<br />\n是以香港家宅不吉，求財不遂。市民為求自身平安，怎能不出入謹慎呢？"},{"pid":"124621319d2ea8129c813df64e9cda01c616e581","tid":1285633,"uid":3560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a627d665759a073126513693389aaf9024a02f4f","tid":1285633,"uid":159568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:08:04.000Z","msg":"常得香腸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:11:46.000Z","msg":"in 廚師腸 we trust <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f85dcbf22e84d06804f556d5445084ddb1a7e2dd","tid":1285633,"uid":231480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:16:18.000Z","msg":"咁係咁邪呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15ae06d4a1092075573361f1cab077f32d425526","tid":1285633,"uid":38119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:17:34.000Z","msg":"留名等其他大師解答<br />\n我記得年頭個陣吹得最勁既就係明日大嶼<br />\n個時簽文入面既石田好多人代左明日大嶼入去"},{"pid":"51819efd3497f43ac83047b5e485450f3a62a818","tid":1285633,"uid":62285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"54a2c9b8f15a1c764e249e929701d0a59fe87bee","tid":1285633,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0eec53782055dff54c059c870bb3f1e52b5c0654","tid":1285633,"uid":62285,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:47:27.000Z","msg":"石田為業喜非常，<br />\n畫餅將來未見香；<br />\n怎曉田耕耘不得，<br />\n那知餅食不充腸。<br />\n<br />\n9up<br />\n某人得到1塊田 好開心， 點知係石田<br />\n畫啲唔香既野食 諗住遲下食， 點知田又種唔到， 野食又唔飽<br />\n<br />\n一場白做<br />\n<br />\n9up mode 屌細力啲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:00:08.000Z","msg":"我好驚係指我哋白做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:18:40.000Z","msg":"正常唔係講市民，講整體政府或者代表"},{"pid":"3cc88b6184d423a7b305f658ec09bca7f61c62d3","tid":1285633,"uid":75647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:21:35.000Z","msg":"車公快來屌㭍777"},{"pid":"1e3986f11e8c5e481b64c51ced78154fb744278f","tid":1285633,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a7320b1c336d0338a3ef721b049eedef73d26c","tid":1285633,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"邊道係石田呢？我覺得唔係明日大愚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"石禮嫌 田北晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"634c8efe32dec140fd1e251d9f0c404664f51216","tid":1285633,"uid":156363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e3986f11e8c5e481b64c51ced78154fb744278f","tid":1285633,"uid":215905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f5a7320b1c336d0338a3ef721b049eedef73d26c","tid":1285633,"uid":3560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T16:22:48.000Z","msg":"邊道係石田呢？我覺得唔係明日大愚"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:37:55.000Z","msg":"石禮嫌 田北晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T17:48:35.000Z","msg":"石田應該係解唔好晒心機啦，點耕作都唔會有成果。送中反對聲音咁大都仲要攬住唔撤回，玩埋D語言偽術。"}]}